'''Kimwaua Makin''' (born 8 August 1997) is a male Kiribati [[sprint (running)|sprinter]]. He competed in the [[2015 World Championships in Athletics – Men's 100 metres|Men's  100 metres event]] at the [[2015 World Championships in Athletics]] in Beijing, China, finishing seventh in his heat.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://media.aws.iaaf.org/competitiondocuments/pdf/4875/AT-100-M-pr----.RS6.pdf|title=Men's  100 metres qualification results|publisher=IAAF | accessdate=29 August 2015}}</ref>  He ran his personal best of 11.77 at the [[Athletics at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics – Boys' 100 metres|2014 Summer Youth Olympics]].

